*task-1.9.3-r1 (20 Nov 2010)

  20 Nov 2010; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org>
  files/task-1.9.2-configure.patch, -task-1.9.3.ebuild, +task-1.9.3-r1.ebuild:
